`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The **uniform RNG call count** pattern is critical here: every `buildQuestContext` call consumes exactly 3 values (npcRoll, targetRoll, amountRoll) regardless of category. For `explore` and `discover`, some rolls are consumed but ignored — this ensures the PRNG stream advances identically for any category, preserving determinism when multiple quests are generated in sequence.
