`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The **deliver template as a 2-step quest** (gather → deliver-to-npc) is the only multi-step procedural quest. This matches how the quest state machine works — `advanceQuestStep` handles both steps through the same state transitions. The deliver pattern could serve as a template for more complex procedural quests (escort, multi-gather, etc.) later.
